author: julianfoad
msg: (svn_fs_fs__begin_obliteration_txn): Change the meaning and name of the
parameter 'rev' (which meant the rev on which the new txn is based) to
'replacing_rev' (meaning the rev that the new txn will become). Expand
above. Rename 'root_id' to 'old_root_id' for clarity. Don't bother
trying to support old TXN_CURRENT formats. Write a doc string and some
above. Note a possible to-do task.
